    <h3 style="text-align:left;">Daffodil Study Forum (DSF) Launched at Daffodil International University </h3>
    <p>
        A new student organization Daffodil Study Forum (DSF) is formally launched on today
        on February 09at Daffodil International University (DIU). Mr. Anisul Hoque, a popular
        novelist and writer was the Chief Guest at the launching program while Md. Sabur Khan,
        Chairman, Board of Trustees, Daffodil International University presided the program.
        Professor Dr. Yousuf M Islam, VC, Daffodil International University, Professor Dr. 
        A M M Hamidur Rahman, Dean, Faculty of Humanities and Social Science, Mr. Sayed Mizanur
        Rahamn, Director of Students Affaires and Mr. Abu Taher Khan, Project Director, IIC also
        spke on the occasion</p>

